19:11.903 --> 19:16.709
He heals a man by the pool in John chapter five.

19:17.369 --> 19:21.754
Now in John chapter six, where everybody else is leaving.

19:21.794 --> 19:24.818
These 12 men

19:25.122 --> 19:35.675
live with a sense of expectancy because Jesus has come through on everything he said he was going to do.

19:35.715 --> 19:37.397
Watch that.

19:37.417 --> 19:46.929
Well, as I make my way to my seat, I'm encouraging everybody to stick with Jesus with a sense of expectancy.

19:48.631 --> 19:51.474
I have not seen all that he's going to do.

19:52.066 --> 19:55.570
ears have not heard all that he's going to do.

19:56.371 --> 19:59.875
My best days are not behind me, but are in front of me.

20:00.656 --> 20:06.182
And I'm sticking with Jesus because I have a sense of expectancy.

20:06.883 --> 20:16.434
No, every day will not be Sunday, but I'm just crazy enough to believe that Jesus is going to do everything he said he's going to do.

20:16.474 --> 20:20.018
High places are going to become low,

20:20.290 --> 20:22.954
