20:27.881 --> 20:32.147
Jesus is going to keep doing what he said he's going to do.

20:33.089 --> 20:34.851
Miracles will take place.

20:35.452 --> 20:38.537
The blind will see the deaf will hear.

20:39.198 --> 20:41.020
Miracles will take place.

20:41.561 --> 20:44.585
Drug addicts will be delivered and liberated.

20:45.106 --> 20:47.730
Miracles are going to take place.

20:47.970 --> 20:50.913
God is not through with us yet.

20:51.613 --> 20:55.857
There's still work to be done in us through us and around us.

20:56.458 --> 21:01.983
And I'm going to stick with Jesus because I have a sense of expectancy.

21:03.344 --> 21:12.293
In this world, you shall have tribulation, but be of good cheer because I have overcome the world.

21:13.054 --> 21:14.495
God is still moving.

21:15.156 --> 21:17.778
