21:20.464 --> 21:25.049
I'm going to my seat, but I got to take it to Calvary on a gun dog Friday.

21:26.090 --> 21:33.637
When they said he was done, when they said the story was over, the disciples had a sense of expectancy.

21:34.538 --> 21:42.345
Everybody else thought they were crazy, but Jesus on the third day was resurrected with all power in his hand.

21:43.226 --> 21:47.250
And if Jesus is going to come through on what he said, he's going to do.

21:48.098 --> 21:52.044
Your best days are in front of you, not behind you.

21:52.945 --> 22:02.520
Watch chapel, stick with Jesus, endure, encourage and expect the Lord to do great things.

22:03.241 --> 22:04.644
